#

Simple Focaccia

40 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-freeDairy-free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Bread

Tags:

BreadEasyHomemade

Description

A soft, fluffy bread with a golden crust, perfect for dipping or as a side dish.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 4 cups
  • warm water: 1 1/2 cups
  • active dry yeast: 2 1/4 teaspoons
  • salt: 2 teaspoons
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • fresh rosemary (or dried): 2 tablespoons
  • coarse sea salt: 1 teaspoon
